item.title: CVE-2022-1404|2024-09-17T03:29:09.010Z -- delta%20electronics -- cncsoft
item.description: Delta Electronics CNCSoft (All versions prior to 1.01.32) does not properly sanitize input while processing a specific project file, allowing a possible out-of-bounds read condition.
